title: Amari Cooper trade talk, MNF recap with Brady Quinn (Football 10/23)
description:
Brady Quinn joins Will Brinson to break down the Monday Night Football matchup between the Atlanta Falcons and New York Giants, and then the guys dive into other storylines from around the league, including the blockbuster Amari Cooper trade, Blake Bortles being benched but now starting in London, the Eagles struggles, Minnesota's smart play calling, the Bills starting Derek Anderson, Arizona firing Mike McCoy and much more.
